{"tid":1914144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"{港共福音}不分化不割席不指責已成過去式","createTime":"2020-03-07T10:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T14:45:29.000Z","uid":283912,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"625fd5d6ccf7b482250db0be33077b2511c8428d","tid":1914144,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T10:25:12.000Z","msg":"上年我地好成功實踐到嘅不分化不割席不指責<br />\n係五毛+熱狗+捉鬼天師嘅努力下已經接近玩完<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>黃色經濟圈變捉鬼大賽</strong></span></span><br />\n偽黃扮黃唔夠黃,真黃又屌人血饅頭<br />\n蝕住做就屌quality唔好,告急就話攬炒預咗<br />\n門檻高出天際,好快圍爐告終<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>泛民原罪論死灰復燃</strong></span></span><br />\n新一輩泛民區軒,許智勇,鄺仔,飛機師...<br />\n一路以黎有咩示威都要親身到場企前線<br />\n到今日都一路follow up嘅唔同案件<br />\n幾個月前連登都appreciate佢地進化咗<br />\n但臨近選舉Fb群組,youtube,連登...<br />\n又出現大量九月懲罰泛民白票風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>放負撚失敗撚橫行</strong></span></span><br />\n六月以黎一直都係各有各做,乜都試咗先<br />\n但近期無論咩行動都被放負撚質疑+叫停<br />\n勇武只會送頭,youtube戰線冇得打<br />\n遊行集會政府唔會理,功能組別冇得贏<br />\n連戰續彪炳嘅cctvb戰線都話冇用唔好做....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>強加人唔同標籤瘋狂割席</strong></span></span><br />\n由we connect全世界變黃營自我孤立<br />\n呢個機構又藍,個個行業又黑,前線得篤尿黃<br />\n和理非=左膠,任何公關/道德考慮就係-0-0<br />\n淺黃同中立都係敵人,港豬罪名仲大過藍絲....<br />\n連正苦有公權力都要做show扮野派錢搶民意<br />\n鄧小強沉迷pr日日黎橫折曲鳩up搶騎牆派支持<br />\n我地乜都冇居然仲可以咁高姿態周圍屌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Youtube戰線未出發先批鬥</strong></span></span><br />\n話打youtube對抗kol100,點知原來係打黃Kol<br />\n劉細良又左膠,李慧玲又鳩up,燒山又廢老<br />\n但新個班文宣巴,Sai Ho,抗爭仔...訂閱又升得慢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府玩足咁多個月打埋開口牌都係想我地割<br />\n而我地過去大半年堅持唔割搞到佢地進退失據<br />\n但樂易玲同寶寶龍一上場似乎真係有d料到<br />\n互屌互割每日上演,士氣一日比一日低落<br />\n加埋連登仔根正苗紅嘅支那內鬥dna <br />\n睇黎距離2016後魚蛋時期嘅大內鬥不遠矣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89590a1469f6d933a866689dd9491cd20fe473d","tid":1914144,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T10:26:00.000Z","msg":"[選戰 = 統計學] 立法會直選，有冇七成議席，就睇你地有冇膽量<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1913635/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1913635/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"07e208bcc1e57d0a3b59bf552fae217374f84fb3","tid":1914144,"uid":286711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T10:28:15.000Z","msg":"香港人受軟唔受硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出晒聲明叫你地割就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca2998e7f7ef689a29896632ac6f59e8cfbd23b","tid":1914144,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T10:29:26.000Z","msg":"「和理非=左膠」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇人講過喎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實上樓主你所講嗰啲嘢多數都係五毛做<br />\n成篇文感覺似係打稻草人多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff541524aa44a8754302b66c1f965974ed8c6b1","tid":1914144,"uid":28391